cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.NI 

This paper is about decentralized machine learning algorithms that aim to reduce communication costs while maintaining convergence and accuracy. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and optimization (cs.DS) techniques, which are commonly used in decentralized machine learning. The paper also discusses the use of ADMM, a control theory method, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper involves communication networks (cs.NI) since it aims to reduce communication costs in decentralized machine learning.
